Pick up the fork and put it in the sink

Turn on the water and wash it
Pick the fork up and carry it to the drawer
Place the clean fork into the drawer

high_descs: Head forward and then turn left to the toaster.

Turn around and bring the fork to the sink.
Wash the fork in the sink.
Bring the cleaned fork back to the toaster.
Open up the drawer in front of the toaster and put the fork in there.

high_descs: Walk straight then turn to the counter on your left
Pick up the second fork from your left
Turn around and go to the sink
Put the fork on the sink and rinse it
Pick up the fork then turn around to your left then move towards the end of the counted
Pull the first cabinet on your left and put the fork inside then close the cabinet
